				<td colspan="2" height="100%" valign="top"><span class="postbody">Is SoW interested in participating in Battlegrounds at all?
<br />

<br />
Seems like a very cool thing for Guilds to do, and a nice way to do controlled PVP. It also takes some of my favorite console video games elements (Dynasty Warriors anyone?) and puts them into a MMO in what looks to be a fun environment.
<br />

<br />
I'm really keen on checking these out, and I know it would be more fun with a group than with random strangers.</span><br /><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
