				<td colspan="2" height="100%" valign="top"><span class="postbody">I think guild participation will depend on how complete the first version of battle grounds is.
<br />

<br />
There were a lot of people complaining that the version on the test server didn't really allow for Raids to enter the same battlegrounds without several hours of wait.  The official Blizzard response was that Battlegrounds will continually see updates and upgrades, but didn't mention a timeline for raid forces to easily enter the same Battle Grounds instance.
<br />

<br />
That was probably a week ago I read that, so everything could have changed by now...  Or perhaps it won't change for months.  Hard to say with how MMO's function.</span><br /><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
